---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="The Lab Bench">
  
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>The Lab Bench</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Personal hardware builds, control systems, and systems infrastructure.</p>
  </div>

  <hr class="divider" />

  <div class="card-grid">
    
    <a href="/projects/homelab" class="card-link">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Proxmox Infrastructure</h3>
        <p>A multi-node virtualization environment leveraging Proxmox for high-availability compute and OPNsense for granular Layer 3 network segmentation. This environment mirrors enterprise-grade security and routing standards.</p>
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span class="tag">Proxmox</span>
          <span class="tag">VLANs</span>
        <span class="tag">Layer 3 Routing</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>
    
    <a href="/projects/argus" class="card-link">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Wireless Signal Audit Rig</h3>
        <p>Custom portable hardware suite designed for RF spectral analysis and mapping wireless network density. The build focuses on high-gain antenna integration and real-time data visualization of signal environments.</p>
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span class="tag">RF Analysis</span>
          <span class="tag">Hardware Integration</span>
          <span class="tag">Signal Processing</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Automated Hydroponic Control System</h3>
      <p>An integrated DWC (Deep Water Culture) system utilizing automated feedback loops for pH and nutrient levels. The system demonstrates real-world application of environmental control logic and sensor integration.</p>
      <div class="skill-tags">
        <span class="tag">Sensor Fusion</span>
        <span class="tag">Closed-Loop Control</span>
        <span class="tag">Embedded Systems</span>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
/* Card Link Styling */
  .card-link {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }
  .card-link:hover .card {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }
  .page-header { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .subtitle { font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .divider { border: 0; height: 1px; background: #dee2e6; margin: 3rem 0; }
  
  .card-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; }
  .card { background: var(--card-bg); border: 1px solid #dee2e6; border-radius: 8px; padding: 2rem; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.02); }
  .card h3 { color: var(--accent); margin-top: 0; }
  .card p { color: var(--text-main); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6; }
  
  .skill-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; margin-top: 1.5rem; }
  .tag { background: #e9ecef; padding: 0.3rem 0.6rem; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-muted); }
</style>